The paper presents a reinforcement learning method based on dynamic programming for an unmanned bicycle. It uses an adaptive critic-based neuro-fuzzy system, which falls under the category of machine learning and robotics. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.RO (Robotics), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
